      <elementaryExchange id="779e4a34-7830-54f6-81cf-b6a1deae84e8" unitId="487df68b-4994-4027-8fdc-a4dc298257b7" casNumber="001333-74-0" amount="0.12747" elementaryExchangeId="8e906def-6bd5-4248-ac2b-94e6eedde3c9" formula="H2">
        <name xml:lang="en">Hydrogen</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">There was no data available on process emissions to air for the production of o-aminophenol. As approximation the air emissions occurring from the purge vent, the distillation vent and fugitive emission sources were estimated to 0.2% of the hydrogen input. The remaining hydrogen is considered to be oxidated to water.</comment>
